def normalise(df, col):
  df[f'{col}_norm'] = (df[col] - df[col].min()) / (df[col].max() - df[col].min())

def create_date_features(df):
  df = df.copy()

  df['dayofweek'] = df.index.dayofweek
  df['quarter'] = df.index.quarter
  df['month'] = df.index.month
  df['year'] = df.index.year
  df['dayofyear'] = df.index.dayofyear
  df['dayofmonth'] = df.index.day
  df['weekofyear'] = df.index.week

  return df

Smoothing PPC_inop¶

First try smoothing by adding di_variance to calculated PCC value

In [ ]:
pcc_smooth = pd.DataFrame(df[['PCC_VALUE', 'LEAKAGE']]).merge(di, how='inner', left_index=True, right_index=True)
pcc_smooth['di_var'] = pcc_smooth['Flow (Ml/d)'] - pcc_smooth['Flow (Ml/d)'].mean()
pcc_smooth['di_var'].describe()

pcc_smooth['PCC_inop_smooth'] = 0
pcc_smooth.loc[pcc_smooth['PCC_VALUE'] > (151.15+pcc_smooth['di_var'])*1.5, 'PCC_inop_smooth'] = 1
pcc_smooth.loc[pcc_smooth['PCC_VALUE'] < (151.15+pcc_smooth['di_var'])*.5, 'PCC_inop_smooth'] = 1

sum_pcc_smooth = pd.DataFrame(pcc_smooth.groupby([pcc_smooth.index])['PCC_inop_smooth'].sum())

sns.lineplot(data=sum_pcc_smooth, x=pcc['month'], y='PCC_inop_smooth', label='DI Variance')
sns.lineplot(data=pcc, x=pcc['month'], y='PCC_inop', label='PCC Inoperable DMAs')
Out[ ]:
<Axes: xlabel='month', ylabel='PCC_inop_smooth'>

This appears to have made operability worse. Try rolling di_var

In [ ]:
pcc_smooth['rolling_di_var'] = pcc_smooth['di_var'].rolling(window=30, min_periods=0).median()

pcc_smooth['PCC_inop_smooth'] = 0
pcc_smooth.loc[pcc_smooth['PCC_VALUE'] > (151.13+pcc_smooth['rolling_di_var'])*1.5, 'PCC_inop_smooth'] = 1
pcc_smooth.loc[pcc_smooth['PCC_VALUE'] < (151.13+pcc_smooth['rolling_di_var'])*.55, 'PCC_inop_smooth'] = 1

sum_pcc_smooth = pd.DataFrame(pcc_smooth.groupby([pcc_smooth.index])['PCC_inop_smooth'].sum())

sns.lineplot(data=sum_pcc_smooth, x=pcc['month'], y='PCC_inop_smooth', label='Rolling DI Variance')
sns.lineplot(data=pcc, x=pcc['month'], y='PCC_inop', label='PCC Inoperable DMAs')

No benefit achieved. Try rolling PCC median with +/- 75%
